    />
    <div class="flex-auto md:flex-1 md:px-5 max-w-2xl" style="">
      <h1 class="text-2xl tracking-tight font-bold">
        {SITE_TITLE}, Software Engineer
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base sm:w-2/3 mt-4 tracking-tight">
        Loves problem solving, always seeking new challenges, outdoors lover. I
        share my development journey through <a
          class="font-semibold underline decoration-purple-600 hover:[text-shadow:0_0_5px_#ffffff]"
          href="https://diegocode.tech/blog/">technical articles</a
